talter geben Gelegenheit zu Ausblick und Perspektiven. Essays zu besonderen Aspekten der Vereinsgeschichte und -gegenwart runden die Darstellung in anschaulicher Weise ab.  aThis work was published to commemorate the 50th anniversary of the VG WORT. It begins with an introduction to the collecting society's development and goes on to describe the collecting society's history from 1958 to 2008. Intrinsically tied to the history of VG WORT are the various intellectual property rights. This work reflects on future prospects in the face of the rapid development of technical advancements and the difficulties in exercising copyright laws in the digital and multimedia age.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aAuthorshipxCollaborationxHistoryx20th centuryxGermany. 0aAuthorshipxCollaborationxHistoryy20th century. 0aCopyright clearinghouseszGermany (West). 0aCopyrightzGermany (West). 0aFair use (Copyright)xGermany. 0aFair use (Copyright)zGermany. 4aVerwertungsgesellschaft /Recht. 7aLAW / Intellectual Property / General.2bisacsh  aCollecting society (law).1 aKoopmann, Helmut, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKreile, Reinhold, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMelichar, Ferdinand, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchade, Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchricker, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aShepherd, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSiebeck, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPA